    <!--[if mso]><style>.mso-logo img{width:180px!important;height:auto!important;}</style><![endif]-->

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <div class="section">
      <p>Hi {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.first_name }},</p>
      <p>Thanks for taking the time to test me out. How did I do?</p>
      <p>As promised, hereâ€™s a summary of our conversation:</p>
    </div>

    <!-- MATTER SUMMARY -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Matter Summary</h2>
      <p>{{ $('AI Agent - Re-write Summary').item.json.output }}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- EXTRA ASSETS INTRO -->
    <div class="section">
      <p>To give you a flavour of what else I can do, Iâ€™ve converted our chat into <b>a few additional marketing assets below.</b></p>
      <p>This is just a snapshot of my capabilities. At&nbsp;<a href="https://legalengine.co.uk/"><b>Legal Engine</b></a>, weâ€™re building a suite of assistants like me, ready to transform Marketing &amp; BD across the legal industry.</p>
