Prompt: Writing as a expert copywriter, and using best practice for UK legal websites, please write me a 150 word posting to appear on my law firm's website as a demonstration of our expertise in this area of law. This should be written in the third person with no header or title. Make sure it acts as a great business development tool to win future work. A recommended format is to identify the problem, highlight the solution we provided and the outcome that was achieved. Do not include any final sentences such as "Trust us to" or "Contact us to" etc. Ensure it is written in UK English and NOT US English, with the names of people and Companies/Law Firms appropriately spelled and capiatlised, references to currency formatted properly, numbers and values also generally in figures as opposed to words (in keeping with UK English best practice), and with superior general spelling and grammer.



INPUT:
The summary of the matter is:{{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.summary }}
The user is:{{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.first_name }} {{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.last_name }}
The user's email is:{{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.user_email }}
The users company or law firm is: {{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.user_email.split('@')[1]}}
Here is the date and time: {{ $now }}
Here is the transcript from the call: {{ $('Webhook1').item.json.body.transcript }}

